PLACEHOLDER — REPLACE WITH YOUR AWS IoT DEVICE CERTIFICATE.

This file is embedded into the firmware (EMBED_TXTFILES) as the mutual-TLS
client certificate. Overwrite it with the certificate you registered for the
Thing (see ../../README.md and ../../../aws-iot/README.md), e.g. the
certificate.pem.crt returned by `aws iot create-keys-and-certificate`.

Do NOT commit a real device certificate/key to a shared repo.
